{
  "info": {
    "name": "ERP — 06 · Commandes (Clients & Fournisseurs)",
    "description": "Collection du module 06 (guide mini-DEV-06).\n\n**Avant de commencer** :\n1. Renseigne la variable de collection `adminPassword` (onglet Variables).\n2. Lance « Auth / Login (admin) ».\n3. Déroule « Prérequis » (client, fournisseur, produit, entrepôt), puis les dossiers DANS L'ORDRE : le flux FOURNISSEUR remplit le stock (10 écrans), le flux CLIENT le consomme, l'annulation le réinjecte, et la conversion ferme la boucle devis → commande.\n\nCycle de vie : `DRAFT → CONFIRMED → IN_PROGRESS → DELIVERED`, annulable partout sauf DELIVERED.\nStock : SORT au `start` (commande CUSTOMER), ENTRE au `complete` (commande SUPPLIER), réinjecté au `cancel`.\n\nEnveloppe de réponse : `{ success, data, meta }` — succès ; `{ success, error: { code, message }, meta }` — erreur.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{accessToken}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:3000/api/v1",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "adminPassword",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "accessToken",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "customerId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "supplierId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "productId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "warehouseId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "supplierOrderId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "customerOrderId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "cancelOrderId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "quoteId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "convertedOrderId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login (admin)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json && json.success && json.data && json.data.accessToken) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', json.data.accessToken);",
                  "    console.log('accessToken enregistré dans les variables de collection.');",
                  "}",
                  "pm.test('Login réussi (200)', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "noauth"
            },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@local.dev\",\n  \"password\": \"{{adminPassword}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Connexion. Le token d'accès (`data.accessToken`) est stocké automatiquement dans la variable `accessToken`."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Prérequis (modules 02, 03, 04)",
      "item": [
